_io", "image_html": null}, {"text": "Самый популярный инструмент ретеншна в iGaming - и главная точка атаки.\n\nSEON: 18% всех потерь от фрода в индустрии - злоупотребление программами лояльности.\n\nПрограмма, которую строили ради ретеншна.\n\n57% операторов: потери от фрода растут быстрее выручки. Уже сейчас.\n\nДо Чемпионата мира 2026 - меньше месяца.\n\nКаждый оффер под Кубок - новая поверхность атаки.\n\nСтроим лояльность. Субсидируем фрод.\n\n@vipcare_io", "image_html": null}], "linkedin_post": {"text": "LINKEDIN POST:\n\nYou spent 6 months building the best VIP loyalty program in your market. Congratulations - you've also built fraud's favorite target.\n\nSEON's Global iGaming Risk & Fraud Report 2026 found that 18% of all iGaming fraud losses come directly from loyalty program abuse. With bonus abuse layered on top, nearly half of all fraud hits the retention stack operators worked hardest to build.\n\nThe uncomfortable number: 57% of iGaming operators report fraud losses growing faster than revenue. Not because acquisition failed - but because loyalty programs became the most predictable attack surface.\n\nNow add the World Cup. Registrations spike. Deposit offers go live. Every promo launched to acquire and retain players during peak season is also an invitation for abuse.\n\nThe best operators are running dual-track: loyalty mechanics visible to players, fraud hygiene invisible to players. Same offer. Different architecture.\n\nMost aren't there yet.\n\nThe World Cup doesn't care about your fraud roadmap.\n\n#iGaming #VIPRetention #CasinoOperations #PlayerExperience"}}